 <div class="section goals" id="goals">
   <div class="container">
     <div class="row">
       <h2 class="main-heading">Research Questions</h2>
       <h5 class="goal-heading">Privacy</h5>
       <p class="goal-description">
         The fundamental research theme of the UCN project is user data privacy and how can we provide advanced content recommendation and delivery services while quaranteeing privacy and keeping users in control of their personal data.
       </p>
     </div>
     <div class="row">
       <div class="one-third column value">
         <h2 class="goal-multiplier">What?</h2>
         <h5 class="goal-heading">Recommendations</h5>
         <p class="goal-description">There is a staggering amount of online content available today on the Internet and finding relevant and interesting content is a daunting task. We seek to build improved content recommendation mechanisms with better knowledge about user’s needs and interests by incorporating various additional explicit and implicit signals originated by the user -- history, habits, mood, location, preferences and so on.</p>
       </div>
       <div class="one-third column value">
         <h2 class="goal-multiplier">When? Where?</h2>
         <h5 class="goal-heading">Context Awareness</h5>
         <p class="goal-description">We own today a multiplicity of networked devices (smartphones, tablets, notebooks, etc.), each requiring different encodings, resolutions, and so on. Furthermore, the manner of accessing the network also changes with time and space (e.g., transition from WiFi to 3G), which introduces additional complexity to the content delivery process.</p>
       </div>
       <div class="one-third column value">
         <h2 class="goal-multiplier">How?</h2>
         <h5 class="goal-heading">Quality of Experience</h5>
         <p class="goal-description">Understanding and improving the user perceived quality of online content delivery is a complex task. How to collect user QoE and relate it to the correct contextual information? How to optimize the content delivery from the Internet based on user context? How to optimize local networking resources according to user context and preferences?
         </p>
       </div>
     </div>
